  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are trapped in heavy short gamma with SPX at 6565.3, sitting right in the heart of massive negative GEX between 6550-6570 strikes, forcing them to buy this rip and amplify the move higher. The breakout regime combined with the wall break and GEX surge suggests dealers will continue aggressive buying into 6600 where they flip to selling pressure at the max positive gamma level. Watch for acceleration through the 6570 resistance wall, but expect meaningful selling pressure to emerge as we approach the 6600 dealer flip zone.\n\n**Bottom line:** dealers must chase this rally higher, expect strong momentum toward 6600.",
